==French==

===Adverb===
'''autant'''
# [[so much]]
#:''Pourquoi travaillez-vous '''autant'''?''
#::''Why do you work so much?''
'''autant que'''
# [[as much as]], as far as
#:''Elle mange deux fois '''autant que''' lui.''
#::''She eat twice as much as him.''
#:''Autant que je le sache,...''
#::''As far as I know,...''
'''autant de'''
# [[as much]], [[as many]]
#:''J'ai '''autant de''' puissance que lui.''
#::''I have as much power as he [does].''

